    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** Notation \"{ x }\" is reserved and has a special status as component\n    of other notations such as \"{ A } + { B }\" and \"A + { B }\" (which\n    are at the same level as \"x + y\");\n    \"{ x }\" is at level 0 to factor with \"{ x : A | P }\" *)\n\n"
